{"tid":2162924,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美民主黨全國代表大會展開　米歇爾指特朗普是錯誤總統","createTime":"2020-08-18T11:18:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-19T02:19:10.000Z","uid":75656,"like":4,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"f0ae375bd5e0eaeae15e28ed363c41e3f372ca92","tid":2162924,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T11:18:10.000Z","msg":"美國民主黨一連四日舉行全國黨代表大會，前第一夫人米歇爾猛烈批評總統特朗普的施政，形容對方是「錯誤的總統」，相反<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>民主黨總統參選人拜登是君子</strong></span></span>，擔任副總統時表現出色，呼籲民眾全力支持拜登，結束特朗普上任以來造成的混亂。<br />\n<br />\n曾經與拜登在初選較量的佛蒙特州參議員桑德斯，亦認為拜登可以結束特朗普導致的仇恨與分裂，以及對移民的妖魔化。共和黨的俄亥俄州前州長卡西奇，亦倒戈支持拜登。<br />\n<br />\n爭取連任的特朗普證實，下星期會在白宮接受共和黨的提名，又形容拜登是一位好悶的人，如果拜登勝選，傳媒將失去聽眾及觀眾。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1544417-20200818.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1544417-20200818.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=4FX4A6L%2BDQn5Srv%2BHBCkF83u7Zzj2Sx3DhCMrptFZ9w%3D&h=bb9bd0aa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1544417-20200818.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=4deae698\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1544417-20200818.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"354772dec7e7ab2f834edf7aaf5f260bf66cf735","tid":2162924,"uid":140552,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T11:19:28.000Z","msg":"君子(偽)"},{"pid":"9d26a9b19a6dd2b0aa2a52e792218695101fae95","tid":2162924,"uid":11703,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T11:22:00.000Z","msg":"Michael又做走出嚟呀"},{"pid":"932b5dccea71b1236607cf835d3bb869f8b48098","tid":2162924,"uid":108199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T11:22:24.000Z","msg":"隻黑雞發咩癲"},{"pid":"2e93470f6c4a108e12fad0375e00bab16b3e3062","tid":2162924,"uid":11703,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T11:22:28.000Z","msg":